Package: countSimEval
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate the similarity of gene expression data
Version: 0.1.0
Author:
  Ruihan Wang[aut,cre]
Description: Input single-cell origin transcriptome data and multiple simulated transcriptome datasets to evaluate their similarity.
    From four aspects: data attributes, ability to simulate cell populations, ability to simulate differentially expressed genes, and ability to simulate cell batch effects.
Maintainer:Ruihan Wang<wangruihan0307@163.com>
